    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1873-11-12T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1873-11-12T00:00:00-05:00" n="731" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d731">
                <head>No. 729.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Fish</persName> to Mr. <persName type="to">Hall</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1873-11-12">
                            <hi rend="italic">November</hi> 12,
                                        1873</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>You will demand of authorities the most ample rights secured by
                                treaty or law of nations for all American citizens on the Virginius.
                                Instruct consul at Santiago to see that they have counsel and
                                advocates, and that he report as to all judicial or other
                                proceedings.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>FISH.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
